  "detailed_description": "<h1>AI Generated Content Disclosure</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Some map visuals in the game were initially generated using AI tools for concept inspiration. These were then extensively edited and manually redrawn to match the game’s unique silhouette-based art style. No AI is used during gameplay or in any real-time game systems.</i></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100 tabby cats in every city. Keep your eyes open.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3740890/extras/095fe1f3cd1534a95035f4e5907f55e8.avif?t=1766986946\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3740890/extras_big/095fe1f3cd1534a95035f4e5907f55e8.avif?t=1766986946 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Stray Tekirs</i> is a relaxing hidden object game where you try to find cleverly hidden <strong>tabby cats</strong> in stylized city silhouettes. The scenes are filled with abstract shapes and layered structures — sometimes just the curve of a tail or the tip of an ear gives them away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗺️ Stylized urban silhouettes inspired by real cities<br>🐾 100 hidden <strong>tabby cats</strong> per map<br>⏱️ Play with a timer or explore freely<br>🎧 A simple, calm, relaxing — and sometimes challenging — experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay focused — some of these tabbies are very well hidden.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100 tabby cats in every city. Keep your eyes open.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3740890/extras/095fe1f3cd1534a95035f4e5907f55e8.avif?t=1766986946\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3740890/extras_big/095fe1f3cd1534a95035f4e5907f55e8.avif?t=1766986946 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Stray Tekirs</i> is a relaxing hidden object game where you try to find cleverly hidden <strong>tabby cats</strong> in stylized city silhouettes. The scenes are filled with abstract shapes and layered structures — sometimes just the curve of a tail or the tip of an ear gives them away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗺️ Stylized urban silhouettes inspired by real cities<br>🐾 100 hidden <strong>tabby cats</strong> per map<br>⏱️ Play with a timer or explore freely<br>🎧 A simple, calm, relaxing — and sometimes challenging — experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay focused — some of these tabbies are very well hidden.</p>",
